üî• Excellent question ‚Äî and a **smart move** if you want to become a **strong JavaScript developer**.

Let‚Äôs go through **all the important functions, methods, and concepts** ‚Äî from **Basic ‚Üí Intermediate ‚Üí Advanced** ‚Äî that you should master.

