## ü™ú Summary Learning Path

| Level                | Focus Areas                                | Estimated Time |
| -------------------- | ------------------------------------------ | -------------- |
| **Beginner**         | Strings, Numbers, Arrays, Functions        | 3‚Äì4 weeks      |
| **Intermediate**     | Objects, DOM, Events, Async, Fetch         | 4‚Äì6 weeks      |
| **Advanced**         | Closures, Promises, ES6+, Modules, Classes | 6‚Äì8 weeks      |
| **Pro JS Developer** | Performance, Design Patterns, Architecture | Ongoing        |

